l 好用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n火牛 550w 足夠？ 底版放唔放得落細機箱<br />\n洗唔洗加風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋洗唔洗加網絡卡<br />\n新手上路 咩都唔識 請多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下小小心意<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/155151_84be95c775848c77d222f13bf0bbcf57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F155151_84be95c775848c77d222f13bf0bbcf57.png&h=cb08c769&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/155152_e1ebd3c649cf54344de060f814d87242.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F155152_e1ebd3c649cf54344de060f814d87242.png&h=3af14bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/155153_8a0a69a103059afc9660f70b20a5f495.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F155153_8a0a69a103059afc9660f70b20a5f495.png&h=975af3c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T08:43:34.000Z","msg":"CPU識唔識超頻?RAM識唔識超?想唔想學?純玩GAME?<br />\n想就繼續,三樣關於超頻既都唔想就直接INTEL<br />\n<br />\nRAM盡量換,GSKILL牌係靚,但點都好用都用TRIDENT Z,本身T字比較好超,反應都夠快,再唔係貴多少少用專門RAM:G.Skill DDR4 Flare X Series 3200MHz 2x8GB F4-3200C14D-16GFX (Special for AMD DDR4) CL值都夠快夠爽,好過你隊條爛鬼野<br />\n另外話就話ZEN2叫做相容好D<br />\n但17年個陣呢隻AEGIS CODE既RAM已經畀人屌到臭<br />\n雖然無人肯定條RAM係一手定二手但個期大把案例講到條RAM好廢,你知七日觀賞期包換或加$換,到時你貪平少少執到條垃圾盞搞到自己<br />\n(＊當年呢隻RAM癲撚到畀人炒起,幾乎賣到兩條1980咁撚嘔心)<br />\n<br />\n底板如果要超<br />\n盡量ASUS<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n火牛唔知你咩牌,但可以講大W數有保證<br />\n砌到7K仲貪平個少少買到件重開機牛盞搞自己<br />\n何況玩得RYZEN 唔超姐係又玩9自己,超得又要預佢2-3年電壓慢慢虧虧地,650內夠啦,最好金牌<br />\n<br />\n最後,唔知你CASE咩型號,無法解答<br />\n都係睇返ATX MATX 呢D代號<br />\n你塊板有M,MA 都可以用落ATX箱,相反你買隻MA箱,買塊ATX板咪隊唔落MA箱度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfecbfb8f31ee4529ae927365b8d39d8b3b43e3","tid":699041,"uid":48673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fff7a733ec5ec3a595c8dc2f3a726fb441459228","tid":699041,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"98a47552a3bfd80438b44a286a46c299d42e8a5d","tid":699041,"uid":48673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T07:52:12.000Z","msg":"小弟想砌返條女 預算$7k左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n預期玩到芒hunt gta 咁。中畫質已經可以 唔洗開到高畫質<br />\n<br />\nCpu: Amd Ryzen 5 2600x<br />\nMb: msi b350 m gaming pro <br />\n顯卡：GTX 1060 <br />\nRam: G.skill F4-3000c16s- 8GISB        DRR4 8Gb x2<br />\nHDD: Toshiba MD04ACA400 (4Tb)<br />\nSSD: Samsumg 970 Evo 250GB M.2<br />\n<br />\n已有mon <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 顯卡方面 3gb 夠唔夠用 洗唔洗轉上去6Gb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nRam 果到一條8gb 夠唔夠行得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定買兩條做duel channel 好用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n火牛 550w 足夠？ 底版放唔放得落細機箱<br />\n洗唔洗加風扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋洗唔洗加網絡卡<br />\n新手上路 咩都唔識 請多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<