kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超頻就可能用落一段時間 就會學下玩下<br />\n想轉會用amd 因為聽落個性價比高過intel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nRam 有冇其他好推介(最少8Gb) 打算用住一條頂下先 有需要再upgrade <br />\n<br />\n底版因爲好少會轉 可以買好啲<br />\nASus TUF B350m-Plus gaming $800-880 or<br />\nASus  prime B350m-k $ 630-680<br />\n<br />\n火牛會用返650w"},{"pid":"ef6bee553fc4a316ae87ce1b4708e03cb004d7ae","tid":699041,"uid":48673,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/184804_ea675cfcbfd326c27de55eebe4e8e8c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F184804_ea675cfcbfd326c27de55eebe4e8e8c3.png&h=23d03009&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/184806_18096f0cfc6def6116c1a8b55ed0ad1b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F184806_18096f0cfc6def6116c1a8b55ed0ad1b.png&h=7d67d5be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/184809_9f06eff3beb0e3f2ca18ef7a2656b192.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F184809_9f06eff3beb0e3f2ca18ef7a2656b192.png&h=6027fcaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/184811_1e3b565b1c20ead00bf4641ad735dc70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F184811_1e3b565b1c20ead00bf4641ad735dc70.png&h=df57454b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ee20dca47441235f6034790ae6ad23ccf41d9e1","tid":699041,"uid":48673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"